[Main Street]
At this point on Main Street, you find yourself midway between the Bazaar and 
Fayd's downtown commercial district. Large gray buildings loom all around you 
and throngs of people swarm back and forth on important business. The scene 
gives you the sense of being small and insignificant among so many.
Obvious exits: south, east, west.
