[Main Street & Elm]
Main Street runs east and west here, intersecting the northern bound Elm 
Street. On the south side of Main is a truly ancient building: a tower that is
taller than any other in the city. It reaches up into the sky like a needle. 
Known as the Tower of Silver Arcana, it headquarters the order of the same 
name. An opening in its side allows entry within. There is a plaque affixed 
above it.
Obvious exits: north, east, west.
