[Pleasant Street]
The Bank of Fayd stands on the west side of the street. This imposing 
structure looks much like a small keep. It has large defensive turrets at its
corners, from which guards keep a vigilant watch. An iron double door allows 
entry. To the north, Pleasant Street intersects with Main Street.
Obvious exits: north, south.
