[Bazaar Northwest]
Grand Avenue, leaving behind its suburban flower boxes, winds into the bazaar
from the north, fetching you up by the cracked dome-shaped structure
previously owned by CyberTech, Ltd. In their labor to recover those arts
known to humankind before the Cataclysm, expert craft technological implants
to improve or replace natural parts of the anatomy for those who can afford
them. An opening in the remains of the building allows entry.
Obvious exits: north, south, east, southeast.
