[Grand Avenue]
A carved sign in the likeness of a golden thimble hangs above the door of a
stately shop. Passers-by pause to look in the door of the shop, where a
mannequin dons the latest in Faydish fashion. Across the street you
notice the glint of metal from an opening between two buildings.
Obvious exits: north, south.
