[Grand Avenue]
Grand Avenue ends here. Looking west down Park Avenue, you see rows of trees
and rioting flowers. Their pleasant hues invite you to take a respite and
rest among them. An ivory white tower leans against the city's walls. Hadan
Kentarus Avenue has begun to make its way northwest of here.
Obvious exits: south, west, northwest.
