[Hadan Kentarus Avenue]
The walkway ends abruptly here, giving way to a path of newly leveled ground.
Grass-covered rubble lies before you, slowly being turned to road by the
city's workers. To the side, a noisy shopped filled with exotic animals has
cropped up.
Obvious exits: southeast.
