w
[Park Avenue]
From beyond a large window, a large calico cat follows your progress along
Park Avenue. As you pass one beautiful home after another, the cat continues 
to gaze at you. When the cat notices you staring back, it suddenly seems to
lose interest in you and begins to clean itself.
Obvious exits: east, southwest.
