sw
[Park Avenue]
The road is in better repair here than anywhere else in the city. Funny how 
that works. The homes here are set back considerably from the street. Little
signs denoting various private security organizations indicate that not all 
are welcome here.
A cottage is here.
Obvious exits: west, northeast.
