[Hardwood Avenue]
As you continue to move along Hardwood Avenue, a particulary old mansion 
reminds you of the rumors you have heard of several of the large estates
being haunted in this section of the city. Some of the ancient beautiful 
estates along the avenue predate even the cataclysm and if spirits prefer
to dwell in any section of town, this is probably it.
Obvious exits: east, west.
> e
e
[Hardwood Avenue]
Hardwood Avenue is one of the most exclusive neighborhoods in all of Fayd. 
Large brick walls and guarded gateways help ensure the privacy of the nobles
who make their home here. The wealth displayed by the elaborate estates is
breath taking. The avenue upon which you travel is made of yellowish bricks
but you feel confident that if the residents of this neighborhood chose to,
they could pave the avenue with bricks of solid gold.
To the west, Hardwood Avenue continues and to the east, Hardwood intersects
Park.
Obvious exits: east, west.
