[Park Avenue]
Lovely homes, seperated from the avenue by well-groomed yards, give this 
section of Park Avenue a cheerful atmosphere. Neighborhood cats prawl the
white-picket fences which seperate the yards. To the southwest, a large
mansion can be seen and past that, the Royal Palace itself is visible.
Obvious exits: northeast, southwest.
