[Park Avenue]
A huge mansion stands before you. Huge white pillars support a roof over the 
breezeway encircling the entire structure. Wide steps lead up to this veranda
and the front door. Strangely, the door is unguarded. From inside come the 
sounds of revelry.
Obvious exits: west, northeast.
